<section id="key-implementation-decisions" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="key-implementation-decisions">Key Implementation Decisions</h2>
<p>When building production risk models, consider:</p>
<ol type="1">
<li><strong>Correlation structure</strong> - How do risks aggregate?</li>
<li><strong>Tail dependence</strong> - Do extreme events cluster?</li>
<li><strong>Computational efficiency</strong> - Can you run enough scenarios?</li>
<li><strong>Validation</strong> - How do you test the model?</li>
</ol>
</section>
